// Old
Calendar calendar = new GregorianCalendar(1990, Calendar.FEBRUARY, 20);
int daysInMonth = calendar.getActualMaximum(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH);

// New
int daysInMonth = YearMonth.of(1990, 2).lengthOfMonth();
```

